descript.abstract: This polygon data layer represents land use for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2004. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waupaca_LandUse_2004.gdb. [This file folder contains the coverage for the County of Waupaca's land use plus all of New London and Marion. It was an update (2003-2005) from the county and their communities. East Central aided in the changes as a service to the county.]
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [The data are created to serve as base information for use in GIS systems for a variety of planning and analysis purposes. Use of data for Engineering work is prohibited.
descript.supplinf:
Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement where applicable. For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://www.co.waupaca.wi.us/landinformation/Data.aspx
[Data have been coded and modified to match ECWRPC Digital Map Data Standards. To obtain a copy, contact the Distributor listed under Distribution Information.]
